{"tid":32183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天空之城？超級罕見球狀「死星」雲驚現日本上空","createTime":"2016-12-10T05:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T02:17:14.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"36e79ada8a134246eb4026261dd466b898adc4ec","tid":32183,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:10:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Cy9EcQhVEAEqJKA.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCy9EcQhVEAEqJKA.jpg%3Alarge&h=0a64e1aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個超級神秘、看起來像星球大戰死星（Death Star）的雲12月4日週日出現在日本上空，罕見的造型讓不少人受到驚嚇！<br />\n<br />\n這顆球狀雲在當天下午3點被發現不祥地漂浮在日本神奈川縣藤澤市的湛藍天空上。<br />\n<br />\n有人將照片發布在Twitter之後，立即受到瘋傳，到目前為止已經有超過20,000人轉推，22,000人喜歡：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/pmxpvrtmx/status/805938180092411905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpmxpvrtmx%2Fstatus%2F805938180092411905&d=Q1Lc9FxxPPjRZGjVx3LN1mN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=de1f1be0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpmxpvrtmx%2Fstatus%2F805938180092411905&h=7d1f0b74\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/pmxpvrtmx/status/805938180092411905</a><br />\n<br />\n一名稱為Poppy的網友上傳這些照片說：「在Facebook上有一則貼文說，週日下午3點，我在湘南台車站看到一個奇怪的雲。肯定的，之前我未曾見過這個...！」<br />\n<br />\n她解釋說，她在Facebook上發現這些照片，詢問貼文者發生了什麼事。<br />\n<br />\n根據報導，他們告訴她，照片未曾加工，神祕球體雲沒多久就被吹散了。<br />\n<br />\n照片貼出後，立刻讓很多人聯想到電影「星際大戰」裡的死星（Death Star），也有人認為它像「天空之城」拉普達（Laputa），許多人都為此感到困惑和擔憂，甚至有人覺得這是不祥之兆。<br />\n<br />\n有一些網友留言表示，當天也有看到球體雲，紛紛對奇特自然現象感到不解。<br />\n<br />\n一名專業網友解釋，那是一個滾軸雲，通常會再低空出現，可以在任何地方出現，但出現機率相當低。<br />\n<br />\n報導也提到，澳洲日前也曾出現一個「牽牛花」雲，造型比球體雲更奇特。"},{"pid":"e5663c3ad8bae425deef0da09ef720c09585c8cd","tid":32183,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪準備炸地球？"},{"pid":"61df2b156996d4568a14d8368a771779a7c13fad","tid":32183,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:14:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪準備炸地球？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n快點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644fd62b2bbe7591a85382a3f79992650d7cd88b","tid":32183,"uid":2203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:15:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪準備炸地球？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n快點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n來吧"},{"pid":"fdeb6e144454dcb74b39e454ad65e71c28d63e9f","tid":32183,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:20:07.000Z","msg":"2012<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dbaf6314b30372e86655443497108030a1a66eb","tid":32183,"uid":62391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:21:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84469b90223ea93038568b859ba24fd7db7da643","tid":32183,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:24:43.000Z","msg":"可唔可以跌個女主角落黎？"},{"pid":"c53378d65daad7e6377104e1028b7ff81bbc798f","tid":32183,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:33:37.000Z","msg":"這帖真屌！"},{"pid":"25db754dc79d81894054ccf8f24695471cceba8d","tid":32183,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:35:09.000Z","msg":"星球大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7384eb56c4e731d19fe3f4f46943f84bce282a","tid":32183,"uid":48274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:36:1